項\r\n傷害人之身體或健康者，處5年以下有期徒刑、拘役或50萬元以\r\n下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c939%2c20220930%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉簡,939,20220930,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"939","JDATE":"20220930","JTITLE":"傷害"}